title: K-Otix: Universal
description:
Group straight out of Houston, Texas, K-Otix goes unnoticed in the rap game. The MCs are Micah and Damien, while Russell "The ARE" Gonzalez handles the DJing. With a more aggressive east-coast vibe to it, this album hits hard but maintains thoughtful lyrics. Straight up ill. Don't miss it.
